org.wso2.carbon.identity.oauth.callback

Class OAuthCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wso2.carbon.identity.oauth.callback.OAuthCallback
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Callback

    public class OAuthCallback
extends Object
implements Callback
    Represents a Authorization callback which represents an authorization action corresponding to authorizing clients to access resources by a resource owners. This callback is used to check whether the given resource owner is the rightful owner to grant authorization to the client to access the given resource.
